parameters:
Orca Asparagus-Mayor: Alright, let's shoot a new adult
video! This time it's an outdoor location... hit the streets
and pick up passersby for some action!!
Memimi: Wha... eh, no, that's... such a thing...

Orca Asparagus-Mayor: You've got a quota of 10 people by the
end of today! Make sure you approach them yourself... If you
go to the hotel in front of the station, just drop my name
and they'll let you use it for free!!

Memimi: Im... impossible... to do it myself, like...
absolutely impossible... ah, no, I don't want to... eek...!

Underling: When I joined the organization, I thought
unifying the city was impossible, but thanks to Lord Shark's
achievements, it's starting to feel real. If you don't
forget hope, anything can happen.

Memimi: You must never give up on your dreams... I will
continue to fight as many times as necessary to achieve my
goal. You all should just believe in me and Lord Shark
Broccoli, and follow us relentlessly...

Underling: (Above all, seeing Lord Shark's various erotic
forms was like a dream come true... The camera in the shower
room has been removed, but I've saved recordings for days
and watched them over and over... I know it's wrong, but
there's no way I can delete the data...)

Memimi: It seems you're trembling with emotion... you've
gone silent...

Underling: To think the mayor would show up... I never
imagined it! That bastard, strutting around so
shamelessly...! And if we lose, Lord Shark Broccoli making
an AV debut?! I really want to see it, but the nerve of
him...!
Memimi: Did I let a bit of my true feelings slip...? Hey...

Underling: This... is a personal gift from me! I bought it
with my own money... "Delicious Powder," please eat it!! As
someone involved in the powder refining business, I can't
let the recipe fall into the wrong hands no matter what...

Memimi: Thank you... I also want to protect the Delicious
Powder. Lord Shark Broccoli's masterpiece, this powder, I
won't hand it over to anyone...

After eating the nutritious powder, you feel revitalized!
Max HP increased by 50!

Underling: Was it three years ago that Lord Shark Broccoli
was picked up by the big boss? This organization was formed
five years ago, and back then, Monster Fight didn't even
exist yet...

Memimi: I've heard that Monster Fight started about two
years ago. The big boss initially didn't intend to bring me
into the dark organization, so I'm not very familiar with
what happened at that time... I joined the organization a
year ago, and my debut in Monster Fight was half a year ago.

Underling: That's a rapid rise... Now Lord Shark Broccoli
has become one of the most important figures in the dark
organization, on the verge of unifying the city... Seriously
amazing...

Memimi: The one I need to repay isn't just Lord Shark
Broccoli... It's also everyone in the organization who has
walked with me and guided me at times. I truly am grateful
to all the people around me...

Underling: You don't have to worry about that...! Just being
able to see you in sexy outfits and being allowed to fondle
your breasts is more than I could ask for...!

Memimi: That wasn't meant as a way of showing gratitude...!
Damn it... I've ended up exposing my shame to close
acquaintances... My personal relationships are... ugh...

Underling: Lord Shark... if Shark Mountain-san loses and has
to debut in an adult video...! I absolutely hate that
idea... I want her to be only mine... I do want to see her
having sex, but only with me, not with anyone else...!!

Memimi: Calm down... that's disgusting!! Stop repeating
'sex' over and over!!

Underling: But even if you say that... just watching her on
TV raping a celebrity in reverse, I felt like I was going to
lose it, and now to think she has to sleep around with other
men as a routine... it does give me a bit of a hard-on,
but...

Memimi: ...Seriously, just shut up... I get how you feel
but...

Underling: At least take this...! It's a heart-shaped
necklace that I chose!! Please wear it and defeat Mayor
Orca...!!

Memimi: Gross... I mean... uh, I'll just accept the
sentiment... thank you...

With the underling's feelings received, Memimi's attack
power increased slightly...
